• ・You have to fight the Guard Leader and two Silver Lobos at the same time.

dungeons.name: Sparring with Kain
dungeons.prologue: Having accepted his offer to train them in order to help them defeat the espers, Tyro and Elarra prepare to spar with Kain.

tip_battle.html_content:
Kain
属性耐性
盾
ブレイク耐性
状態異常耐性
Poison / Silence / Paralyze / Confuse / Slow / Stop / Reflect / Blind / Sleep / Petrify / Doom / Instant KO / Berserk / Sap / Interrupt
tip_battle.title: Kain (Destruction)
tip_battle.message:
• ・Use only physical attacks.
  • ・Uses group physical attacks.
  • ・When it loses HP, its Attack and Speed rise, and its Defense and Resistance fall.

  • –Key Strategy–
  • ・Use Protect to raise your heroes' Defense.
  • ・Protect wears off after a few turns, so try refreshing it while it's still in effect.
  • ・Tap to select an ability's target.
  • ・Use summon magic attacks when Resistance is low.
  • ・Try setting Battle Speed to 1.

dungeons.name: Antlion's Den 2
dungeons.prologue: Tyro, Elarra, and Prince Edward part ways with Tellah and continue to explore the cave in search of the Antlion's Nest.

tip_battle.message:
• ・Use only physical attacks.

dungeons.name: Mist Cave
dungeons.prologue: After defying the king's orders, Cecil and Kain head for the village of Mist, accompanied by Tyro and Elarra. Along the way, they are attacked by a Mist Dragon in the cavern that leads to the village.

tip_battle.html_content:

tip_battle.title: Mist Dragon (Destruction)
tip_battle.message:
• ・Uses group physical attacks.
  • ・Enters Mist form after three turns in Normal form.
  • ・Enters Normal form after one turn in Mist form.
  • ・Always counterattacks with Freezing Mist in Mist form.

  • –Key Strategy–
  • ・Use Shell to raise your heroes' Resistance.
  • ・Try not to attack while it's in Mist form.
  • ・Try setting Battle Speed to 1.

dungeons.name: Antlion's Den 1
dungeons.prologue: The Octomammoth defeated, Tyro and Elarra's party finally arrive at Damcyan. Once there, they soon learn that Tellah's concerns were all too real.

dungeons.name: Underground Waterway 1
dungeons.prologue: Cecil, Tyro, and Elarra find themselves reunited with Rosa in Kaipo. They next decide to head for the underground waterway in search of the Antlion's Den.

dungeons.name: Mobliz 2
dungeons.prologue: The ancient monster Humbaba threatens the village of Mobliz once again. Just when Tyro and Elarra seem hopelessly outmatched, Terra shows up to assist them.

tip_battle.html_content:

tip_battle.title: Humbaba (Destruction)
tip_battle.message:
• ・Uses magic attacks that damage one target in the front row.

  • –Key Strategy–
  • ・The Soul Gauge does not fill during this battle. In exchange, you can use Soul Breaks as soon as the battle begins.
  • ・Use the Finding Love Burst Soul Break to enter Burst Mode, boosting stats and transforming Attack and Defend into special abilities for several turns.
  • ・Use Faith to raise your heroes' Magic.
  • ・Use Heathen Frolic to lower the enemy's Magic.

dungeons.name: Underground Waterway 2
dungeons.prologue: During their travels, Tyro, Elarra, and the others meet Tellah the sage. Upon learning that he too is traveling to Damcyan, they decide to join forces and make their way through the Underground Waterway together.

dungeons.name: Midgar Sector 1
dungeons.prologue: Tyro discovers mysterious paintings in an area where strange magic has been detected. Thus begins an all-new chapter in the struggle to protect the records.

dungeons.name: West Mines 1
dungeons.prologue: The strange light emitted by the frozen Esper and Terra cause Tyro and Elarra to pass out. When they awaken, they find themselves in a house back in Narshe.

dungeons.name: Mako Reactor No. 1
dungeons.prologue: Tyro finds himself daunted at seeing the great tales of history come to life before his eyes. With Elarra back to her senses, the two keepers make their way through Mako Reactor No. 1 together with Cloud and AVALANCHE.

dungeons.name: Underground Waterway 3
dungeons.prologue: Tellah tells Tyro, Elarra, and the others of a sinister air that hangs over Damcyan. Tyro and Elarra's party make haste towards their destination, only to find an enormous monster blocking their path.

dungeons.name: Kaipo
dungeons.prologue: Though concerned about Kain's whereabouts, Tyro and Elarra manage to arrive at the village of Kaipo along with Cecil and a young girl, the last of the summoners.

tip_battle.title: General＆Baron Soldier (Destruction)
tip_battle.message:
• ・You have to fight the General and the three Baron Soldiers at the same time.
  • ・Use only physical attacks.
  • ・Baron Soldier B uses group physical attacks that deal damage proportional to current HP.
  • ・The General flees once all Baron Soldiers are gone.
  • ・Once the General is gone, the Baron Soldiers attack each other.
  • ・Defeat all enemies, or defeat all Baron Soldiers and make the General flee to win the battle.

  • –Key Strategy–
  • ・Ignore the General and defeat the Baron Soldiers.
  • ・Use Weak Polka to lower all enemies' Attack.
    • ・Baron Solider B uses group attacks, so defeat him first.
  • ・Use Slow to lower the General's Speed.
  • ・Use Soul Breaks like Darkness and Cyclone Grimoire that deal group attacks.

dungeons.name: Midgar Sector 8
dungeons.prologue: Having successfully destroyed Mako Reactor No. 1, Tyro and Elarra decide to stick with Cloud in order to learn more about their current circumstances. Shortly afterwards, they bear witness to a fateful encounter between two great heroes.

dungeons.name: Mako Reactor No. 1 Assault
dungeons.prologue: Together with AVALANCHE, Tyro and Elarra help Cloud destroy Mako Reactor No. 1. As the bomb's timer ticks down, the group hurries to make their escape.

tip_battle.title: Guard Scorpion (Destruction)
tip_battle.message:
• ・Use only physical attacks.
  • ・Enters Tail Raised form after three turns with its tail down.
  • ・After one turn in Tail Raised form, it lowers its tail again.
  • ・Always counterattacks with Tail Laser in Tail Raised form.

  • –Key Strategy–
  • ・Use Power Break to lower the enemy's Attack.
  • ・Use Boost to raise your heroes' Attack.
  • ・Use Cure to restore HP after taking damage.
  • ・Try not to attack it while it's in Tail Raised form.
  • ・Try setting Battle Speed to 1.

dungeons.prologue: Tyro and Elarra find a new Corrupted Painting thanks to the sudden appearance of Chococheep. Within that record, they meet a former soldier fighting tirelessly to achieve her goal.

dungeons.name: Narshe
dungeons.prologue: Tyro and Elarra find themselves in Narshe, a mining town that is rumored to house a frozen esper. It is here that they meet a young girl under the control of the Gestahlian Empire.

dungeons.name: Airship
dungeons.prologue: Tyro, Elarra, and P'soon discover a new Corrupted Painting, wherein they encounter a hero who commands the Red Wings airship fleet for the kingdom of Baron.

dungeons.name: Figaro Castle
dungeons.prologue: Driven by a desire to aid Terra, Elarra decides to join Tyro in battle. Together with Locke and the moogles, Tyro and Elarra manage to escape the mine and make their way to Figaro Castle.
